FROM [AbpUserOrganizationUnits] AS [a]

    SELECT [a0].[OrganizationUnitId], [a0].[RoleId]
    FROM [AbpOrganizationUnitRoles] AS [a0]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [a0].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [a0].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_2)
) AS [t] ON [a].[OrganizationUnitId] = [t].[OrganizationUnitId]

    SELECT [a1].[Id], [a1].[Name]
    FROM [AbpRoles] AS [a1]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [a1].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [a1].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_2)

SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[BusFeePlanId], [s].[Notes], [s].[Status], [s].[StudentId], [s].[SubscriptionDate], [s0].[Id], [s0].[Grade], [s0].[MobileNumber], [s0].[Name], [s0].[PreviousAmount], [s0].[Status], [s0].[StudentId], [b].[Id], [b].[ExpectedTotalAmount], [b].[FullAmountDueDate], [b].[FullAmountWith5PercentDiscount], [b].[Line]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Grade], [t].[MobileNumber], [t].[Name], [t].[PreviousAmount], [t].[Status], [t].[StudentId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[AmountPaid], [t0].[EducationalInstallmentId], [t0].[InvoiceNumber], [t0].[IsFullPayment], [t0].[PaymentDate], [t0].[PaymentStatus], [t0].[PaymentStatusLastUpdate], [t0].[StudentId], [t0].[TransactionId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[DueDate], [t0].[EducationalFeePlanId], [t0].[Order], [t1].[Id], [t1].[BusFeePlanId], [t1].[Notes], [t1].[Status], [t1].[StudentId], [t1].[SubscriptionDate], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[AmountPaid], [t1].[BusInstallmentId], [t1].[BusSubscriptionId], [t1].[InvoiceNumber], [t1].[IsFullPayment], [t1].[PaymentDate], [t1].[PaymentStatusLastUpdate], [t1].[Status0], [t1].[TransactionId], [t1].[Id00], [t1].[Amount], [t1].[BusFeePlanId0], [t1].[DueDate], [t1].[Order]
FROM (
    SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[Grade], [s].[MobileNumber], [s].[Name], [s].[PreviousAmount], [s].[Status], [s].[StudentId]
    FROM [Students] AS [s]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s0].[Id], [s0].[AmountPaid], [s0].[EducationalInstallmentId], [s0].[InvoiceNumber], [s0].[IsFullPayment], [s0].[PaymentDate], [s0].[PaymentStatus], [s0].[PaymentStatusLastUpdate], [s0].[StudentId], [s0].[TransactionId], [e].[Id] AS [Id0], [e].[Amount], [e].[DueDate], [e].[EducationalFeePlanId], [e].[Order]
    FROM [StudentEducationalPayments] AS [s0]
    LEFT JOIN [EducationalInstallments] AS [e] ON [s0].[EducationalInstallmentId] = [e].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[StudentId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s1].[Id], [s1].[BusFeePlanId], [s1].[Notes], [s1].[Status], [s1].[StudentId], [s1].[SubscriptionDate], [t2].[Id] AS [Id0], [t2].[AmountPaid], [t2].[BusInstallmentId], [t2].[BusSubscriptionId], [t2].[InvoiceNumber], [t2].[IsFullPayment], [t2].[PaymentDate], [t2].[PaymentStatusLastUpdate], [t2].[Status] AS [Status0], [t2].[TransactionId], [t2].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t2].[Amount], [t2].[BusFeePlanId] AS [BusFeePlanId0], [t2].[DueDate], [t2].[Order]
    FROM [StudentBusSubscriptions] AS [s1]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [s2].[Id], [s2].[AmountPaid], [s2].[BusInstallmentId], [s2].[BusSubscriptionId], [s2].[InvoiceNumber], [s2].[IsFullPayment], [s2].[PaymentDate], [s2].[PaymentStatusLastUpdate], [s2].[Status], [s2].[TransactionId], [b].[Id] AS [Id0], [b].[Amount], [b].[BusFeePlanId], [b].[DueDate], [b].[Order]
        FROM [StudentBusPayments] AS [s2]
        LEFT JOIN [BusInstallments] AS [b] ON [s2].[BusInstallmentId] = [b].[Id]
    ) AS [t2] ON [s1].[Id] = [t2].[BusSubscriptionId]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[StudentId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]

FROM (
    SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[Grade], [s].[MobileNumber], [s].[Name], [s].[PreviousAmount], [s].[Status], [s].[StudentId]
    FROM [Students] AS [s]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s0].[Id], [s0].[AmountPaid], [s0].[EducationalInstallmentId], [s0].[InvoiceNumber], [s0].[IsFullPayment], [s0].[PaymentDate], [s0].[PaymentStatus], [s0].[PaymentStatusLastUpdate], [s0].[StudentId], [s0].[TransactionId], [e].[Id] AS [Id0], [e].[Amount], [e].[DueDate], [e].[EducationalFeePlanId], [e].[Order]
    FROM [StudentEducationalPayments] AS [s0]
    LEFT JOIN [EducationalInstallments] AS [e] ON [s0].[EducationalInstallmentId] = [e].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[StudentId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s1].[Id], [s1].[BusFeePlanId], [s1].[Notes], [s1].[Status], [s1].[StudentId], [s1].[SubscriptionDate], [t2].[Id] AS [Id0], [t2].[AmountPaid], [t2].[BusInstallmentId], [t2].[BusSubscriptionId], [t2].[InvoiceNumber], [t2].[IsFullPayment], [t2].[PaymentDate], [t2].[PaymentStatusLastUpdate], [t2].[Status] AS [Status0], [t2].[TransactionId], [t2].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t2].[Amount], [t2].[BusFeePlanId] AS [BusFeePlanId0], [t2].[DueDate], [t2].[Order]
    FROM [StudentBusSubscriptions] AS [s1]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [s2].[Id], [s2].[AmountPaid], [s2].[BusInstallmentId], [s2].[BusSubscriptionId], [s2].[InvoiceNumber], [s2].[IsFullPayment], [s2].[PaymentDate], [s2].[PaymentStatusLastUpdate], [s2].[Status], [s2].[TransactionId], [b].[Id] AS [Id0], [b].[Amount], [b].[BusFeePlanId], [b].[DueDate], [b].[Order]
        FROM [StudentBusPayments] AS [s2]
        LEFT JOIN [BusInstallments] AS [b] ON [s2].[BusInstallmentId] = [b].[Id]
    ) AS [t2] ON [s1].[Id] = [t2].[BusSubscriptionId]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[StudentId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]

INFO  2025-07-07 22:05:04,688 [62   ] oft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command - Executed DbCommand (52ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Grade], [t].[MobileNumber], [t].[Name], [t].[PreviousAmount], [t].[Status], [t].[StudentId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[AmountPaid], [t0].[EducationalInstallmentId], [t0].[InvoiceNumber], [t0].[IsFullPayment], [t0].[PaymentDate], [t0].[PaymentStatus], [t0].[PaymentStatusLastUpdate], [t0].[StudentId], [t0].[TransactionId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[DueDate], [t0].[EducationalFeePlanId], [t0].[Order], [t1].[Id], [t1].[BusFeePlanId], [t1].[Notes], [t1].[Status], [t1].[StudentId], [t1].[SubscriptionDate], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[AmountPaid], [t1].[BusInstallmentId], [t1].[BusSubscriptionId], [t1].[InvoiceNumber], [t1].[IsFullPayment], [t1].[PaymentDate], [t1].[PaymentStatusLastUpdate], [t1].[Status0], [t1].[TransactionId], [t1].[Id00], [t1].[Amount], [t1].[BusFeePlanId0], [t1].[DueDate], [t1].[Order]
FROM (
    SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[Grade], [s].[MobileNumber], [s].[Name], [s].[PreviousAmount], [s].[Status], [s].[StudentId]
    FROM [Students] AS [s]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s0].[Id], [s0].[AmountPaid], [s0].[EducationalInstallmentId], [s0].[InvoiceNumber], [s0].[IsFullPayment], [s0].[PaymentDate], [s0].[PaymentStatus], [s0].[PaymentStatusLastUpdate], [s0].[StudentId], [s0].[TransactionId], [e].[Id] AS [Id0], [e].[Amount], [e].[DueDate], [e].[EducationalFeePlanId], [e].[Order]
    FROM [StudentEducationalPayments] AS [s0]
    LEFT JOIN [EducationalInstallments] AS [e] ON [s0].[EducationalInstallmentId] = [e].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[StudentId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s1].[Id], [s1].[BusFeePlanId], [s1].[Notes], [s1].[Status], [s1].[StudentId], [s1].[SubscriptionDate], [t2].[Id] AS [Id0], [t2].[AmountPaid], [t2].[BusInstallmentId], [t2].[BusSubscriptionId], [t2].[InvoiceNumber], [t2].[IsFullPayment], [t2].[PaymentDate], [t2].[PaymentStatusLastUpdate], [t2].[Status] AS [Status0], [t2].[TransactionId], [t2].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t2].[Amount], [t2].[BusFeePlanId] AS [BusFeePlanId0], [t2].[DueDate], [t2].[Order]
    FROM [StudentBusSubscriptions] AS [s1]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [s2].[Id], [s2].[AmountPaid], [s2].[BusInstallmentId], [s2].[BusSubscriptionId], [s2].[InvoiceNumber], [s2].[IsFullPayment], [s2].[PaymentDate], [s2].[PaymentStatusLastUpdate], [s2].[Status], [s2].[TransactionId], [b].[Id] AS [Id0], [b].[Amount], [b].[BusFeePlanId], [b].[DueDate], [b].[Order]
        FROM [StudentBusPayments] AS [s2]
        LEFT JOIN [BusInstallments] AS [b] ON [s2].[BusInstallmentId] = [b].[Id]
    ) AS [t2] ON [s1].[Id] = [t2].[BusSubscriptionId]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[StudentId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]

FROM (
    SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[Grade], [s].[MobileNumber], [s].[Name], [s].[PreviousAmount], [s].[Status], [s].[StudentId]
    FROM [Students] AS [s]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s0].[Id], [s0].[AmountPaid], [s0].[EducationalInstallmentId], [s0].[InvoiceNumber], [s0].[IsFullPayment], [s0].[PaymentDate], [s0].[PaymentStatus], [s0].[PaymentStatusLastUpdate], [s0].[StudentId], [s0].[TransactionId], [e].[Id] AS [Id0], [e].[Amount], [e].[DueDate], [e].[EducationalFeePlanId], [e].[Order]
    FROM [StudentEducationalPayments] AS [s0]
    LEFT JOIN [EducationalInstallments] AS [e] ON [s0].[EducationalInstallmentId] = [e].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[StudentId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s1].[Id], [s1].[BusFeePlanId], [s1].[Notes], [s1].[Status], [s1].[StudentId], [s1].[SubscriptionDate], [t2].[Id] AS [Id0], [t2].[AmountPaid], [t2].[BusInstallmentId], [t2].[BusSubscriptionId], [t2].[InvoiceNumber], [t2].[IsFullPayment], [t2].[PaymentDate], [t2].[PaymentStatusLastUpdate], [t2].[Status] AS [Status0], [t2].[TransactionId], [t2].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t2].[Amount], [t2].[BusFeePlanId] AS [BusFeePlanId0], [t2].[DueDate], [t2].[Order]
    FROM [StudentBusSubscriptions] AS [s1]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [s2].[Id], [s2].[AmountPaid], [s2].[BusInstallmentId], [s2].[BusSubscriptionId], [s2].[InvoiceNumber], [s2].[IsFullPayment], [s2].[PaymentDate], [s2].[PaymentStatusLastUpdate], [s2].[Status], [s2].[TransactionId], [b].[Id] AS [Id0], [b].[Amount], [b].[BusFeePlanId], [b].[DueDate], [b].[Order]
        FROM [StudentBusPayments] AS [s2]
        LEFT JOIN [BusInstallments] AS [b] ON [s2].[BusInstallmentId] = [b].[Id]
    ) AS [t2] ON [s1].[Id] = [t2].[BusSubscriptionId]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[StudentId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
